                        <i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle"></i>
                        <span>Hasta <strong>2,000 alumnos activos</strong></span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="feature-item">
                        <i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle"></i>
                        <span>Optimización de Base de Datos SQL</span>
